subSubSection.paragraph: This species is widely distributed in the Holarctic (e.g., Whitfield 2006 , Fernandez-Triana 2010 , Yu et al. 2012 , Fernandez-Triana et al. 2014 ). Here we present new and detailed information about the distribution of the species in Canada, including one new provincial record (ON), based on examined specimens from the BIO and CNC collections. Data for those specimens was extracted from BOLD.
